xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 22 , ( by yue shaoyan ) - the central bank 's policy committee on the 22 nd decided to maintain the current financial policy , with the total amount of funds provided to the market still maintaining the level of 15 - trillion yen ( 1 - trillion yen ) .
on the issue of the government and the ruling party 's demand for " formulating an appropriate inflation target , " the meeting held that the government should adopt a prudent attitude .
the meeting held that although japan 's economic prospects have become more covert , the stock market and financial market have been relatively stable , and the economic situation has not changed , and therefore it has decided to maintain the current financial policy .
on the question of the government and the ruling party urging the central bank to further relax the bank and set a suitable target of inflation , the central bank held that the current financial market in japan is very sufficient .
if there is insufficient capital supply in the financial market in the future , the central bank will increase the amount of capital input in accordance with the need .
