shenzhen customs cracks down on monetary smuggling
xinhua news agency , shenzhen , january 25 , ( by li nanling and li xiangzhi ) - while ensuring the effective supervision of civilization , shenzhen customs has dealt a severe blow to the smuggling of currency through the inspection channels .
last year , the customs handled a total of 1,023 monetary cases , with a total value of more than 15,000 yuan , of which 15 cases ( not including foreign exchange bills ) were handled .
as the largest tourist inspection port in the country , the lo wu customs is responsible for the supervision and control of more than 25,000 passengers a day , and it is likely that there will be a considerable amount of money outflow every day if it is not strictly controlled .
in the face of such a situation , the customs authorities have always adopted strict supervision and inspection measures to investigate the situation and to strictly guard against the outflow of currency in the country .
at 9 : 00 a.m . on 19 february last year , a middle - aged woman , carrying li boxes and flying fast , attracted the attention of the customs officers .
after the luggage , the customs officers found that there were suspicious objects inside the box , and they found that the cart was in a black plastic bag , with a total of $ 3 million .
this is the largest case in which tourists were seized in the past two years , and this is the largest case in which they were flying outside the country .
in july and august last year , the " underground qian zhuang " attempted to make use of the flow of passengers at the lo wu summer festival to enter and leave the country . the port is a crowded opportunity for the people on the spot to steal a large amount of foreign currencies .
the customs has attached great importance to this , and has deployed manpower on the spot to resolutely crack down on " underground cash smuggling " activities .
from 2 july to 1 august , the lo wu customs seized four " underground cash " smuggling cases , with a total value of more than 146,000 yuan .
tibetan new year delegation meets in new year
xinhua news agency report of january 27 from lhasa ( by staff reporter rabin ) on the afternoon of the 27 th , the lhasa hotel was in a festive atmosphere , and more than 3,000 people from all walks of life and all walks of life in tibet attended the spring festival and the tibetan new year meeting held here .
at the meeting , legqog , chairman of the tibet autonomous regional people 's government , called on the people of all nationalities in the whole region to work hard for all the builders of the qinghai - tibet railway , the officers and men of the people 's liberation army , the armed police , and the public security officers and men of the tibet autonomous region , as well as the chinese new year greetings to the tibetan compatriots abroad .
he said : in the past year , with the cordial concern of the party central committee and the state council , and with the selfless support of the people of all ethnic groups in the whole country , especially the provinces , municipalities , and key state - owned enterprises , the autonomous region party committee and government have united and led the people of all ethnic groups in the region to uphold the guiding ideology of the work in tibet in the beginning of the new century , united in a pioneering spirit , and maintain the sustained , rapid , and healthy development of the national economy .
tibet has shown a good situation in which the people are united and the people , the economy is developing , the society is advancing , the people of all nationalities are united , the situation is stable , and the people are living and working in peace and contentment .
he pointed out : the new year is the first year for tibet to comprehensively implement and implement the spirit of the 16 th party congress , and is also a key year for tibet to promote development by leaps and bounds and to lay a foundation for building a well - off society in an all - round way .
tibet will comprehensively promote the healthy and coordinated development of socialist material civilization , political civilization , and spiritual civilization in tibet .
at the meeting , the tibet autonomous regional song and dance troupe and other units presented excellent performances .
pagbalha geleg namgyai , vice chairman of the npc standing committee , attended the meeting .
german council for promoting peaceful reunification president jiang 's eight - point proposal on taiwan
xinhua news agency , berlin , january 27 , german overseas chinese and chinese people of chinese origin issued a statement on the 26 th to mark the eighth anniversary of president jiang zemin 's important speech entitled " continue to strive to promote the accomplishment of the great cause of the reunification of the motherland . "
the statement reviewed the development course of cross - strait relations and the many actions taken by the overseas compatriots in recent years to " oppose separatism , oppose taiwan independence , and promote the peaceful reunification of the motherland , " and held that compatriots on both sides of the strait have carried out full and effective cooperation .
the statement said : president jiang zemin 's important speech is a solid foundation for the establishment of a benign interaction and cooperation between the chinese people on both sides of the strait and overseas compatriots . it has both the core of the one - china principle , and the chinese people on both sides of the strait are a brotherly love of the times , and has a clear - cut characteristics of the times , and also a very strong reality , and has the flexibility , and stability of the final settlement of the problem .
the statement pointed out : president jiang 's eight - point proposal has fully safeguarded and represented the most fundamental interests of the chinese people on both sides of the strait and overseas compatriots .
the statement called on overseas compatriots to make new efforts to promote the reunification of the motherland .
chinese culture festival opens in ankara
xinhua news agency , ankara , january 28 ( reporter zheng jinfa ) - the " chinese culture festival " with the theme of " the chinese people celebrating the chinese spring festival " was opened at the trade center in the turkish capital of ankara on the evening of the 28 th .
hebei province 's song and dance performance , acrobatic skills and other brilliant programs have attracted more than 15,000,000 turkish viewers .
in the evening , many of the viewers went to the hall to get the best seats .
the performance was not yet beginning , and many of the viewers had no choice but to stand on the corridor of the hall , and many children had no choice but to see the performance of the chinese actresses .
the dance " running mule " with local characteristics in hebei shows the interest of young husband and wife on the way back to their home .
turkey 's viewers have been full of laughter for the excellent performance of the actors and their humorous remarks , and they have been warmly applauded .
when china 's singing artist zhai fang sang singing and singing the famous " big mountains " of turkey , the whole scene was a thunderous applause .
at the end of the performance , many turkish viewers rushed to taiwan to ask chinese actors and actresses to sign up , and some of them had a group photo taken to mark the occasion , and some turkish children had left their tears because they had not been signed or had a group photo taken by the chinese actors .
a turkish girl told xinhua : " i saw such a beautiful chinese dance for the first time .
i hope that all kinds of chinese opera groups will come to turkey to perform , so that our turks will have a better understanding of chinese culture . "
( hong kong , macau , taiwan ) mainland residents gradually become major buyers of hong kong chin bank
xinhua news agency , hong kong , january 29 , the head of the administrative department of the hong kong week of the people 's republic of china , guanxi ( hong kong ) , said that the mainland visitors have become the main source of tourists from hong kong .
he said that during the christmas holidays last year , the consumption of domestic customers accounted for three to 40 percent of the total amount of gold in hong kong , becoming a major consumer in the hong kong gold industry .
in early 2002 , the number of mainland visitors coming to hong kong increased significantly after the opening of the travel restrictions for mainland visitors .
last year , during the lunar new year , the labour day , the 11 th golden week and christmas holidays , mainland visitors brought along the retail market in hong kong , especially the high - grade consumer goods market in hong kong .
the relevant authorities in hong kong estimated that about 600,000 mainland visitors will come to hong kong this year , and many businesses , especially high - grade shops , have placed their eyes on how to consolidate and expand the mainland 's passenger market .
the company is expected to increase its sales volume by 5 percent during the spring festival .
in order to meet the needs of mainland visitors , some companies have started to change their operational methods and strategies , and many companies have stepped up their training of staff to learn putonghua , and have introduced courses from time to time to enhance their service attitude and level .
in general , the old card is not allowed to purchase any discounts , but now as long as mainland visitors pay cash , they will be offered preferential treatment to attract more mainland customers .
