xinhua news agency , phnom penh , january 29 ( reporter lei bethong and zhang ruling ) over 1,000 cambodian people rushed into the thai embassy in cambodia on the evening of the 29 th , setting fire to the thai national flag and vehicles , and setting fire to the embassy building .
cambodia 's police are trying to control the situation and are mobilized to fire several fire trucks .
at present , the cambodian police have no way to confirm whether there are casualties .
the protest started on the morning of the same day , in protest against a thai movie star named surnamed " wu gobi is thailand . "
after that , more and more protesters gathered at the thai embassy in cambodia to burn the tire car , the thai national flag , and the thai female stars , and then the protesters dashed into the embassy .
in addition , suzuki has made a statement to reporters in thailand , denying that he had made such a remark that " the cave is thailand . "
