xinhua news agency , paris , january 29 ( reporter wang jingcheng ) french foreign minister de villepin announced at the parliamentary hearing on the 29 th that france had sent military reinforcement troops to cote d'ivoire to ensure the implementation of the peace agreement reached by various parties in cote d'ivoire and the strengthening of french peacekeeping forces .
de villepin did not reveal the number of reinforcement troops .
however , he said , france has taken all necessary measures to ensure the safety of overseas chinese in cote d'ivoire .
he said : with the support of the international community , france will undertake the obligations of supervising the implementation of the peace agreement in cote d'ivoire and make efforts to restore the authority of cote d'ivoire and safeguard its territorial integrity and the implementation of the agreement .
de villepin said that the peace agreement reached by various parties in cote d'ivoire on 24 april " is the most reliable guarantee for realizing peace and national reconciliation in cote d'ivoire . "
in order to promote the implementation of the peace agreement , he has maintained close contacts with president barbuda and other political parties of kuwait .
he said that the three - day flights between abidjan and paris had been resumed on the 29 th .
( international ) nicaragua holds rallies against us war against iraq
xinhua news agency , antigua , january 30 ( reporter yang wenzheng ) several hundred anti - war people held a demonstration and rally in front of the us embassy in nicaragua on the 30 th to strongly oppose the possible us military strikes against iraq .
the organizers of this assembly , the " nicaragua peace promotion association " chairman , made a speech at the meeting , condemning the united states for grabbing iraq and attempting to launch a war of aggression against iraq .
the demonstrators from the capital , melons , vegetables , and other cities held various kinds of placards , loudly shouting slogans such as " do n't america 's war against iraq , want world peace , " and so on , asking the united states to immediately stop all kinds of war preparations .
in a letter to the us embassy , demonstrators said : " let us jointly fight for the future of world peace , freedom , and prosperity , and let us learn to respect others ' rights , and the iraqi issue should be resolved by iraq under the constructive assistance of the international community . "
u.s. consumer spending increases well in 1996
xinhua news agency report of january 31 from washington ( by staff reporter wang zhenhua ) - the us department of commerce released a report on january 31 st , although individual consumption in the united states showed a relatively rapid growth in january last year , the annual growth rate was only the same as the 2001 economic recession .
in the last month of last year , consumer spending in the united states grew by 0.9 percent , the biggest increase since last july .
spending on durable goods increased by 6.1% , while spending on non - durable goods and services grew by 0.2% .
this is a clear indication of the unactive us holiday consumption in the peak season .
in the last quarter of last year , consumer spending , which accounted for about two - thirds of the gdp of the united states , increased by only 1 percent , which was clearly lower than the 4.2 percent growth rate in the third quarter of 1993 , the lowest in the first quarter of 1993 .
economic analysts believe that this is mainly because the united states may launch a war against iraq , a sharp fall in the stock market , and a slowdown in the employment market . this is the most important reason for the sharp slowdown in the us economy in the fourth quarter .
for all of last year , consumer spending in the united states increased by 4.5 percent , the same as in 2001 .
the report said that personal incomes in the united states increased by 0.4 percent in january last year .
for all of last year , personal incomes in the united states increased by 3 percent , which was lower than the 3.3 percent increase in 2001 .
the u.s. savings ratio declined from 4.5 percent in november to 4.1 percent at the end of the year , as the increase in consumer spending was higher than the increase in income .
( international ) palestinian army attacked in cote d'ivoire
xinhua news agency , abidjan , january 31 , a french soldier in cote d'ivoire was attacked by the local protesters at the abidjan airport on the 31 st , and about 800 young cote d'ivoire youths were thrown to the french army soldiers , causing serious injuries to one french army soldier .
since the leaders of west african countries held talks in senegal on the civil war in cote d'ivoire , the situation in cote d'ivoire has escalated .
in cote d'ivoire 's political arena , the respected sydow jones was nominated as the new prime minister at the meeting , and will return to china to set up a coalition government on the 31 st .
however , the " young patriot " organization , which supports cote d'ivoire 's president barbuda , has been displeased with the armed forces in the future , and the minister of national defense and internal affairs .
they accused france of accepting the government 's plan , and claimed that dialla is " the french prime minister , " and threatened to be waiting for the death of tediya .
according to reports , although the runway of the arapache airport have been cleared and cleaned up , hundreds of " young patriot " members are still staying in the waiting hall , and they are ready to resist dialla 's return to china .
the cote d'ivoire civil war lasted for four months and hundreds of people were killed in the conflict .
the french ministry of foreign affairs suggested on the 31 st that 16,000 french nationals residing in cote d'ivoire withdraw as soon as possible .
( international ) canada 's two astronauts fei junshi
xinhua news agency , ottawa , february 3 ( reporter hu guangyao ) according to local media reports on the 3 rd , due to the crash of the us " columbia " space plane , two canadian astronauts will suffer setbacks in may and november this year .
canadian space agency director and the first astronaut in canada said that the us investigation into the " columbia " incident may cause obstruction to the international space station , and some plans may be postponed or even cancelled .
canadian astronauts mclam and williams originally scheduled to take off in may and november this year respectively .
they are now undergoing training in houston .
in canada , three astronauts took part in the space flight mission by the " columbia " in the 2090 s .
snow also revealed that during the " colombia " space science experiment , two of the space scientific research projects were sponsored by canada .
these studies involve the growth of protein , one of which is to be used for the treatment of breast cancer and the other in front - line carbonic cancer .
according to another report , after the crash of the " columbia " , the us space agency immediately shortened the training of a astronauts in canada .
seven astronauts who had received training at the military base in the city of ramallah , canada , have returned to the united states last week .
( international ) us construction spending up markedly in december last year
xinhua news agency report of february 3 from washington ( by staff reporter he young ) - the us department of commerce said in a report on the 3 rd that us construction spending rose by 1.2% in january last year over the same period of last year , and the seasonally adjusted annual rate of 85.3 billion us dollars .
the report said that the seasonally adjusted annual rate of housing construction spending in january was 4.34 billion us dollars , an increase of 2.9 percent over the same period last year .
analysts believe that the low interest rate level is an important factor leading to the strong growth of housing construction .
at present , the us federal reserve is still keeping short - term interest rates stable at 1.2 percent , the lowest in the past 41 years .
however , the contrast between real estate and housing construction is that , after a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 158.6 billion us dollars in january last year , a drop of 1.9 percent over the same period last year .
analysts believe that there are factors of instability in the us economic prospects , and enterprises are unwilling to increase investment in factories and other facilities .
in addition , the worry about terrorist attacks has also adversely affected commercial building activities . although bush signed a terrorist insurance bill in november last year , it is not enough to eliminate the worries of investors .
for the whole year of last year , the growth rate of residential building expenditure in the united states dropped from 2.7% in 2001 to 0.4% , the lowest since 1991 .
( international ) un inspectors found another air chemical warhead in iraq
xinhua news agency report of february 4 from baghdad ( by staff reporter wang bo ) - the un weapons inspection group spokesman said in a press release on the 4 th that the inspectors found another chemical warhead in the spot of the iraq suspicious .
he said that the inspection personnel found the air - to - air chemical warhead in the taji , located in the northern suburbs of baghdad .
the warhead was affixed with a label and was kept in good order .
he said that the warhead is similar to the 12 air - to - chemical warheads found in a military ammunition depot in southern iraq on january 16 .
soon after the inspection personnel found that the chemical warheads were approved , the iraqi side announced that it had discovered four similar warheads in the taji area and handed them to the inspection personnel .
in a report to the security council on 27 january , the chairman of the un inspection , monitoring , and inspection commission , the iraqi government said that the iraqi government should take the initiative to give an account of the chemical warheads in its weapons report , and should not seek the inspection personnel .
on the same day , the inspection personnel also inspected seven locations in the vicinity of baghdad , including a water purification facility , an agricultural chemical factory , two missile factories , and one of the centers used to develop chemical weapons .
the inspection team , located in northern iraq 's northern city of mohammed , inspected a sugar factory and a parent production plant on the 4 th .
the shanghai police confirmed that the two crash victims were turkish men
xinhua news agency report of february 10 from shanghai ( by staff reporter yang jinzhi ) - the shanghai police confirmed that two men , aged 20 in karachi and 19 , were the residents of turkey .
at 10:58 on 23 january , the shanghai municipal public security bureau took the " 110 " report to the police , claiming that an air hijacking incident occurred in shen hong village , an old hong kong town in the south , and two foreign men , from the south to the north , fell from a plane that was ready to land .
after the on - the - spot investigation and investigation work , the shanghai police soon made an assessment and confirmed that the deceased was found to have been in the air from the plane of the fao - 112 , and the result was confirmed by the air .
since then , the shanghai police have conducted cooperation and investigation with the french and turkish consulate general and the police of the above - mentioned two countries .
in early february , according to the information provided by the two deceased 's corpse and the identity card of the turkish police , the shanghai police , after technical comparison , confirmed the fingerprints of the two deceased , and eventually confirmed the true identity of the two deceased .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) macao 's budget surplus 13 percent last year
xinhua news agency , macao , february 10 ( reporter li jie ) according to the news from the macao special administrative region government , macao 's fiscal budget for the year 2002 is good , with a total surplus of 1.7 billion patacas ( about 13 percent of the annual budget ) , which is equivalent to 13 percent of the fiscal budget .
according to sources , the budget for the 2002 macao fiscal year was originally a budget deficit of 8.7 billion macao dollars .
after deducting the surplus in 2001 , the amount of the equator of the macao yuan was also 300 million yuan , which is expected to be used to make up for the year .
however , the special administrative region government has opened up new sources of revenue and the actual income has increased by about 10 percent over the budget , and the actual expenditure is 8 percent less than the budget .
financial secretary ecevit said that the increase in macao 's budget for 2002 was mainly due to the successful opening up of the gambling industry , the telecommunications industry , and the recovery of the real estate industry .
statistics show that the amount of betting duty in 2002 increased significantly over 2001 , and the number of subscribers in the telecommunications industry increased by a large margin , and the property market has become more active , and the number of property transactions has increased by 30 percent .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) macao passed a bill to avoid double taxation
xinhua news agency , macao , february 11 , the macao special administrative region ( sar ) legislative council passed a bill on the 10 th to confer the power of the chief executive of the sar to sign a double taxation agreement .
the so - called " double taxation " refers to the fact that two or more tax jurisdictions are collecting the same or similar tax on the same tax , the same time , and the same tax .
the bill believes that once a double taxation situation occurs in macao , the chief executive of the hong kong special administrative region ( sar ) has the right to take necessary measures to standardize the inter - regional agreement on the avoidance of double taxation .
the legislative council members , who are responsible for examining the " international or regional taxation system " bill , said that the trend of global economic integration is becoming more and more obvious , and the tax system must keep pace with it as soon as possible . otherwise , it will restrict the flow of funds , goods , and personnel .
the signing of the agreement on the avoidance of double taxation between macao and other regions is conducive to the attraction of macao 's foreign capital , and is also conducive to macao 's foreign investment , and is an important link in promoting economic development .
according to sources , there are already two agreements between macao and portugal on the avoidance of double taxation and the signing of agreements with the mainland . it is expected that an agreement can be reached in the middle of this year .
( fax from hometown of overseas chinese ) quanzhou becomes " china 's production base for japanese goods "
xinhua news agency report of february 12 from fuzhou ( by staff reporter wang zhongkang ) - quanzhou , a region with a relatively fast development of china 's private economy , has recently become a " china 's daily production base for the production of goods , " and the relevant departments have recently held a grand ceremony to give the cards and the ceremony .
the title of the " china daily production base " is the province 's new town , and a new town of the former national hero zheng chenggong , the central part of the nanan city , and the coastal economic development zone in southern fujian .
the town was founded in 1999 , with a total area of 61 square kilometers , 11 administrative villages , 450,000 people , and more than 20,000 overseas chinese and hong kong , macao , and taiwan compatriots .
the province has now formed a complete industrial chain with the focus on the development of the japanese - made products industry .
there are more than 70 japanese - funded enterprises in the whole town , with fixed assets reaching more than 300 million yuan , and more than 10,000 people are engaged in the production and sales of daily goods , with an annual export volume of nearly 200 million yuan .
the main products include a variety of plastic bags , color bags , and the plastic bags , and the food products and the health care of women , such as a meal , a plastic bag , and a plastic bag , and the children 's outdoor products , and several hundred products , including the united states , canada , europe , and southeast asia .
in 2002 , the output value of the industrial and commercial industry of this town reached 5.04 billion yuan , accounting for 70 percent of the total industrial output value of the whole town , and the industrial and commercial tax revenue totaled 140.08 million yuan , accounting for 67.1 percent of the total amount of tax paid by the whole town .
( international ) france makes recommendations to the security council on strengthening inspections on iraq
xinhua news agency , united nations , february 11 ( reporter guo lijun ) - the french permanent mission to the united nations on the 11 th issued a proposal on strengthening the inspection of iraqi weapons to the security council members .
france has proposed to double the official personnel to carry out weapons inspections in iraq in the near future , and will gradually increase the number of inspectors and eventually reach three times .
at present , there are about 110 formal inspectors in iraq .
france also suggested that the united states step up air reconnaissance or use the un security forces to ensure the " freeze " of suspicious locations in iraq , and use mobile customs inspection teams to step up inspection of iraqi goods .
france also suggested that a new intelligence agency in new york be responsible for coordinating the operations of various countries to the united nations monitoring , inspection and inspection commission and the international atomic energy agency .
it demanded that the two organizations take the importance of the disarmament task of iraq , which has yet to be completed .
in iraq , arrangements are being made to communicate with iraqi officials daily .
france distributed its proposal in the form of " non - document . "
france and russia have expressed their views in this form during the consultations on the 1441 resolution .
according to the relevant provisions of the security council , the official sex of this " non - document " is weak in the draft resolution , but it can be upgraded to a draft at any time under the request of the country .
according to diplomatic sources here , the content of the french proposal did not exceed the content of the speech made by us secretary of state colin powell on five days after listening to us secretary of state colin powell 's intelligence briefing . this " non - document " is a summary and training of france 's stand on the iraqi inspection issue at the request of some member states of the security council .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) mainland tourists have strong consumption capability in macao
xinhua news agency , macao , february 14 ( reporter li jie ) in recent years , the number of mainland tourists coming to macao has not only increased , but also increased the consumption power .
according to the official statistics released by the macao special administrative region ( sar ) government , in the fourth quarter of last year , foreign tourists spent 4.7 billion patacas ( about 33.3 million u.s. dollars ) in the macao special administrative region ( sar ) .
since the mainland relaxed its foreign tourism policy last year , the number of mainland tourists taking part in " visiting hong kong and macao " and " overseas visits " outside hong kong and macao has increased rapidly .
of the 1.553 million tourists received last year , 42.4 million were from the mainland , and the number of tourists coming to macao for the first time in the fourth quarter of last year has exceeded the number of tourists from hong kong and macao .
although these tourists stayed in macao for only 28 hours , their average per capita spending reached 2560 patacas ( 64% ) , an average of 64% higher than the average of tourists in various places .
the analysis shows that jewellery , watches and clothing materials are the most popular commodities purchased by tourists from all over the world , accounting for 27 percent and 23 percent of their consumption in australia .
of the non - shopping consumption , the average spending on consumer goods , including betting , is $ 837 per person , and the eating and accommodation are two main items , accounting for 41% and 36% .
( international ) research finds obstacles to early production
xinhua news agency report of february 15 th from washington ( by staff reporter li wei ) - the general intellectual development is slow in the early years of the production , and it is easy to encounter obstacles to study .
researchers at yale university in the united states recently found that with the growth of age , this study obstacle can be overcome .
the study has confirmed that the nerve system , which has less than 1,500 grams of early birth , is easy to have problems , of which 50 percent are special assistant when the children go to school .
although many experiments showed that animals were able to resume their brain damage in the early days , they had never seen any relevant reports about the recovery of brain damage .
according to reports by the media here , the research personnel of yale university have been tracking and observing 300 early - stage production , and conducted the tests of the intellectual property of the three , four , six , and eight years old . they have found that the majority of the people have been moving along with the passage of time , and their ability to learn has been constantly improved .
the test said that early - stage production of the three - year - old " intellectual obstacles " was included in the examination of language understanding and intellectual property rights in five years .
however , 23 percent of the babies have left serious brain damage due to brain damage , and the situation of intellectual development has not changed .
researchers said that one of the key factors in the early development of intellectual resources lies in the family environment .
the results of the tests were higher than those of the children 's intellectual property , who had received tertiary education from the family and the mother .
japanese investment development network in shenyang by bell
xinhua news agency report of february 16 from shenyang ( by staff reporter shi qingwei ) - the japanese bell network corporation recently signed an agreement with the management committee of the shenyang city new area to set up a joint venture enterprise , planning to invest 3 billion yen in the development of soft and hard - looking networks in the new south area .
according to sources , the first phase of this joint venture project will be completed between april 2003 and march 2005 , and by 2005 , the number of enterprise staff will reach 3,000 , and it will become an important base for the development of soft and hard telephone networks in northern china .
according to the experts concerned , china 's viewing network technology is still in the development stage , while japan 's bell network corporation is in the world 's leading position in this field , and the project has a good prospect for development in china .
the japan bell network corporation was founded in 1989 . it was a new japanese company that mainly engaged in the development of computer network hardware , production , and network communications services . last year , it was sold to 12.4 billion yen .
shenyang city , liaoning province is an economic center in northeast china .
wang likun , vice mayor of shenyang city , said that the development of the south - south new area is an important technology industrial base in north china . at present , more and more foreign countries have settled down in the south .
( international ) chile , china sign mou on the implementation of animals and plants
xinhua news agency , santiago , february 17 ( reporter hou yaobang ) - the state administration of quality inspection of china and the chilean ministry of agriculture signed a memorandum of understanding on the implementation of health and plant health measures here on the 17 th .
under the memorandum , the two sides will formulate the requirements for the entry and exit of animals and plants , as well as the world organisation for animal health , the " international convention on the protection of plants " and the codex , and the inspection and quarantine of the animals and plants .
according to the mou , the two sides should strictly abide by the inspection and quarantine requirements signed by the two countries , implement the inspection and quarantine work on the import and export of animals and plants , animal and plant products , and food , and strengthen market access for animals and plants and food on a scientific basis , and carry out the inspection and quarantine of the above - mentioned products .
the mou was signed by ge zhirong , deputy director of the state administration of quality inspection and the state administration of chile , and the acting director of the chilean ministry of agriculture .
euro zone 's trade surplus up to 102.3 billion euros last year
xinhua news agency , brussels , february 19 ( reporter feng jian ) the latest statistics released by the european union ( eu ) statistics bureau on the 19th showed that the euro zone 's foreign trade surplus was 102.3 billion euros in 2002 , an increase of more than double the previous year .
the report showed that the trade surplus of the euro zone in 2001 was 49.5 billion euros .
last year , the trade surplus of the 15 eu countries was 6.1 billion euros .
the report said that the sharp decline in imports was mainly due to the growth in the trade surplus .
according to statistics , compared with 2001 , the euro zone and the eu 's overall imports decreased by 4 percent , while exports increased by 1 percent .
in the first 11 months of 2002 , imports from japan and the united states declined by 12 percent and 11 percent respectively , while exports to japan and switzerland declined by 6 percent .
among the eu member states , the biggest trade surplus was germany , with a trade surplus of 117.9 billion euros , while britain was the biggest trade deficit in the eu member states .
the number of financial cases in shanghai and zhejiang decreased to the lowest point in 13 years .
xinhua news agency report of february 20 from shanghai ( by staff reporter wang hongyang ) - the number of financial cases in the second provinces and municipalities of shanghai and zhejiang , which are located in the forefront of china 's financial and trade center and financial reform and opening up , decreased by 44.4 percent over the previous year , and the number of cases involved in the case decreased by 22.8 percent and the number of cases decreased to the lowest point in 13 years .
according to the latest news from the shanghai branch of the people 's bank of china , in recent years , the financial sector in various localities in shanghai and zhejiang have comprehensively improved the investigation and prevention system of financial cases , effectively checked the trend of the high occurrence of financial violations and law - breaking cases , and brought about a good situation in which the number of cases involved in the case , the amount of money involved , and the number of major cases in the past .
statistics show that compared with the previous year , the number of financial cases in the two provinces and municipalities decreased by 22.9 percent and 35.4 percent respectively in 1999 , and the amount involved in the case decreased by 41% and 11.2 percent respectively , and the amount of money involved in the case decreased by 35.4 percent in 2001 .
it has been learned that various localities in shanghai and zhejiang have established five cases of " investigating , educating , reform , and supervision " that are in line with the characteristics of the local financial industry . at the same time , they have also coordinated with various banking , insurance , and securities companies ' internal business functions , supervision departments , and local judicial organs to form a network for preventing the socialization of financial cases .
( international ) eu to suspend imports of paraguay beef
xinhua news agency , buenos aires , february 20 ( reporter shen an ) - the european union ( eu ) has decided to suspend the import of paraguay beef due to the existence of the foot - and - mouth disease in paraguay on the 20 th .
according to paraguay media reports , paraguay paraguay 's minister of agriculture and animal husbandry , announced the eu 's decision at the meeting on the 19 th .
in early february , the inspection group of the european commission 's food and veterinary office submitted a report on the inspection of paraguay , saying that the measures taken by paraguay in the control of the foot - and - mouth disease are still not enough , and there are " serious problems " in the control and inspection system , whether in terms of health control , professional and technical level , and the system of export certificates are not in line with the eu 's requirements .
paraguay is the first case of foot - and - mouth disease in october last year , and after that , with the help of other members of the south common market , it has adopted preventive and control measures .
paraguay exported 60,000 tons of beef each year , mainly export brazil and chile .
these countries have ceased to import paraguay beef .
from january to october last year , the eu imported 567 tons of beef from paraguay .
( international ) austrian researchers find spillage stem cells leading to chronic diseases
xinhua news agency , vienna , february 20 ( reporter lin chuan ) - the researchers of the austrian university of vienna found a group of nerve stem cells with a long memory of the human backbone , and these stem cells were strongly excited , and this has taken another step forward in looking for chronic diseases .
chronic diseases are extremely sensitive to the pain of the patients , and they must finally have to bear hardships and pain in their daily life .
so far , however , people have almost no idea about the cause of illness .
according to a report by the austrian news agency , the research group , led by the director of the nerve of the vienna university 's brain research institute , found that some backbone stem cells did not perform in the normal circumstances , and that they would be very excited when they were inspired by the pain .
the pain has been strong enough , and the reaction has been enhanced .
however , different from other nerve cells , this group of backbone stem cells has become too sensitive to the pain of the pain , and even if the pain is not trivial , it will be greatly stimulated .
scientific research personnel also found that there is a special channel in the bone marrow , and when the stem cells are stimulated , they will be opened , and the calcium will be further triggered by chain reaction .
sanjiu believes that the reason why the chronic illness has been a minor pain , and that this kind of nerve cell in the bone marrow has a long memory and has preserved the " pain signs . "
he said that this discovery could guide people to find ways to eliminate this memory .
china 's consumer price rises in january
xinhua news agency report of february 21 from beijing ( by staff reporter liu dongkai ) - the state statistical bureau 's monthly situation report on the 21 st showed that the overall level of consumer prices in january rose 0.4 percent over the same period last year , the first increase in the past 12 months , against the background of a continuous decline in the past 12 months .
the national bureau of statistics said that the increase in the overall consumer price level was mainly due to the difference between the spring festival of january and february last year , and the peak period of the spring festival in february and the spring festival , so there was a certain amount of uncertainties .
another reason was that the weather was cold this year than last year .
of the 31 provinces , municipalities , and autonomous regions that were investigated , the overall level of consumer prices of 22 residents increased as compared with the same period of last year , and the remaining seven declined compared with the same period last year .
statistics show that among various types of consumer goods , the prices of consumer goods and services such as vegetables , fruits , and cultural entertainment have increased , while the prices of grain , clothing , durable , and other consumer goods have been falling for a long time .
the increase in gasoline and diesel oil prices has driven the liquefied petroleum gas price to continue to rise .
china publishes first chinese middle and primary school education tv series
xinhua news agency report of february 21 from haikou ( by staff reporter zhang chuanzhao and liu wei ) - - - - china 's first " middle and primary school education knowledge lecture " tv series , which was broadcast in haikou a few days ago , has evoked strong repercussions among teachers and students .
the sex education series , which was published by the hainan provincial electronic audio and video publishing house , is divided into a small , medium , and high - grade edition .
according to the knowledge of sex at different stages of age , it has been introduced in a gradual and orderly manner , including special topics such as the youth spring period , pregnant women , child protection , aids protection , and sexes , and has answered questions in the children 's hearts .
on the first of its kind held at the zhenfa school in hainan province , more than 100 primary and middle school students seriously watched and had a silence .
in the beginning , many girls only looked low and did not raise their heads and later gradually watched the picture .
lai ruxing , president of the school , said that the school needs such sex education materials , and it has resolved the embarrassment of teachers and students .
the appearance of this set of lines has also been affirmed by relevant departments .
in november 2002 , the " lecture on the knowledge of the middle and primary school education " was awarded the 10 th china population and culture award presented by the state family planning commission and the china population and culture promotion association .
chinese citizens to malta for tourism to begin in late march
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 22 ( reporter qian chunzheng ) - the chinese citizen 's delegation to malta will leave for malta on march 28 .
chinese tourists can make a leap forward in the travel of the two continents in 10 days .
at that time , tourists can take off from beijing by boarding the flights of the egyptian airline , playing five days in cairo , and flying to malta .
it is estimated that the regiment will pay about 16,000 yuan in 10 days .
malta is located in southern europe and is approaching italy .
the beautiful scenery of the blue sea and the blue sky , as well as the warmth of the geodetic climate , have made it a famous tourist destination in the world .
egypt is one of the four great civilizations in the world , and it has a long history to attract tourists from all over the world .
malta became the first chinese citizen to travel in europe in 2001 , and egypt became the first chinese citizen to travel by himself .
egypt 's first direct flight route from cairo to beijing was officially opened in january this year .
the delegation is jointly launched by the malta national tourism administration , the egyptian tourism administration , and the guangzhou international travel service .
