xinhua news agency , united nations , february 22 , according to a report by the media here on the 22 nd , the chairman of the united nations monitoring , inspection , and inspection commission ( supervision committee ) , hanley , chairman of the un monitoring , inspection , and inspection commission , has already made an ultimatum to iraq , asking iraq to start destroying its " saber " missile in a week .
the spokesman for the control yuan , the spokesman for the nuclear news agency , said that the cox had already issued an ultimatum to iraq 's permanent representative to the united nations , asking iraq to start to destroy this kind of illegal weapon before 1 march .
an ultimatum has been submitted to the un security council .
according to the experts concerned , this ultimatum made the iraqi president saddam is facing a difficult situation in which he is facing .
the destruction of these missiles will result in iraq 's loss of important weapons of defense against the united states , and the refusal of the nuclear regulatory commission 's request will enable the united states and britain to take military action against iraq under the pretext of the united states and britain .
in his second report on the iraqi weapons inspection report submitted to the un security council on 14 april , the chief secretary - general of the international atomic energy agency , elbaradei , said that the missile range of the " sabri " missile has exceeded 150 km and has violated the relevant resolutions of the security council .
( international ) the president stressed that he would try to prevent chechen 's illegal armed forces from entering the pan - pearl river valley
xinhua news agency , moscow , february 24 ( reporter dong longjiang ) - in his speech on the 24th in georgia 's state radio station , georgia 's president shevardnadze stressed that the most important task of the government of georgia is to prevent and completely stop the chechen illegal armed elements from sneaking into the pan - pearl river valley .
shevardnadze said : during the special operation conducted by georgia 's interior troops , police units , security departments , and the ministry of national defense in the autumn last year , the foreign armed forces , which had sneaked into the pan - hexi valley , have been able to remove some illegal armed elements who have been hiding in the bashexi valley in the capacity of refugees .
shevardnadze said that georgia 's strong departments are capable of discovering these illegal armed elements .
at the same time , he also announced that strong departments will continue to take action to crack down on illegal armed forces in the panxi valley in the near future .
in his speech , shevardnadze stressed the importance of cooperation and exchange of intelligence between russia and the united states on this issue .
the border between the two countries is located in georgia and russia in the region of chechnya .
russia believes that georgia is hiding a large number of chechen rebels and accused them of providing asylum .
last year , the relations between russia and georgia were tense for a time due to the pan gexi valley issue .
