xinhua news agency , beijing , february 25 ( reporter wu jing ) - the china red cross society opened its telephone and donations on the 25 th to appeal to all sectors of the society at home and abroad to help the xinjiang compatriots who were hit by the earthquake on the 24 th .
china red cross society donated 010-651399 ( 24 hours on duty )
account number : china industrial and commercial bank of china 2000010-14-52 sub - division
the chinese red cross society urgently dispatched 250,000 yuan to the xinjiang disaster area after the quake on the 24th , and dispatched a disaster relief team to the disaster areas on the 25 th .
on the 24 th , an earthquake measuring 6.8 degrees occurred in the southern part of the xinjiang uygur autonomous region .
